Introduction

A-Jax was a five-member boy group from DSP Entertainment. The final member lineup consisted of Dowoon (formerly Hyeongkon), Yunyoung, Seungjin, Seungyub, and Jonghee.

A-Jax debuted on June 1, 2012, and officially disbanded on March 31, 2019.
